==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Parietes
<hw>Pa*ri"e*tes</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>paries</ets> a wall.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>The walls of a cavity or an
organ; <as>as, the abdominal <ex>parietes</ex>; the <ex>parietes</ex> of
the cranium.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>The sides of an ovary or of a
capsule.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Parietic</ent>⟦br⟧
